PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Consumer and Corporate Affairs of David B. Watters, of Kanata, Ontario, as a member of the Standards Council of Canada; and designation of the said David B. Watters as a member of the executive committee of the Standards Council of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Jean Gariépy, whose term has expired.
